{"id":232669010,"title":"#心得 玉山 U Bear快速核卡 脫離小白","content":"職業：一般行政\n年資：三個月\n年齡：23\n申請卡片：玉山 U Bear卡\n年收入：填40萬\n提供之財力證明：郵局 & richart 活存 共約10萬\n學貸：無，感謝父母🙏\n已持有卡片：無\n核卡額度：3萬\n\n申辦過程：\n11月事先跟玉山專員聯絡，收到申請簡章跟回郵信封\n上星期工作滿三個月領薪後立即寄出\n\n12/6（五）\n掛號寄出（有個資怕寄丟）\n12/9（一）\n查郵局已經寄到\n12/11（三）\n下午1點 收到簡訊已入件建檔\n下午4點 在公司接到照會電話，送電腦評分\n晚上9點 收到簡訊已核卡，嘗試綁定玉山Wallet 成功\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpP.jpg\n\n額度只有三萬有點小詫異，但其實短期內沒要出國也夠用了XD\n玉山動作之快真的讓人嚇到，當天入件當天核卡😂\n\n其實我還有申請Richart gogo，但昨天被婉拒了QQ\n我們公司人數不多，是領現，我都當天拿去存郵局\n（一個信封裝幾萬現金，會計說每次發薪日他都很挫XD）\n聽說台新很吃薪轉，不知道是不是因為這原因\n\n以上給大家參考~~","excerpt":"職業：一般行政，年資：三個月，年齡：23，申請卡片：玉山 U Bear卡，年收入：填40萬，提供之財力證明：郵局 & richart 活存 共約10萬，學貸：無，感謝父母，已持有卡片：無，核卡額度：3","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"de2af8b3-8fd5-4864-9ac1-4351e579821a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-11T16:22:34.018Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T16:26:41.171Z","commentCount":1,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["小白","玉山","核卡","信用卡"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"信用卡","forumAlias":"creditcard","school":"東海大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":12},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpP.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"ba046b0d-40a3-404a-95d2-4e7a3cdf87ec","url":"https://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpPl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpPl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpPl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-11T16:25:52.299Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-11T16:26:41.171Z"},{"id":"ba046b0d-40a3-404a-95d2-4e7a3cdf87ec","url":"http://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpP.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/bXbAmpP","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/bXbAmpPl.jpg"